<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-08-06T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-08-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="805" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d805">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Constantinople</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-08-06"><hi rend="italic">August 6, 1896</hi></date>.
                                (Received Aug. 20.)</dateline>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 941.]</seg></opener>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that it was
                            deemed prudent to send the inclosed telegram to each mission post in the
                            interior.</p>
                        <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">A. W. Terrell.</hi></signed></closer>
                        <pb facs="0953" n="859" xml:id="pg_859"/>
                        <frus:attachment>
                            <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Inclosure in No,
                                941.—Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to
                                        <gloss type="to">Missionaries</gloss>.</hi></head>
                            <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Constantinople</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-08-05"><hi rend="italic">August 5, 1896</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                            <p>Are you properly guarded? Do you wish guards to continue? Telegraph
                                or write all your wants and dangers to me direct.</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Terrell.</hi></signed></closer>
                        </frus:attachment>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>